session_description: This is an example description for a session.
Basic overview of the Angular JS Framework
With increasing number of device sizes Apple now supports the usage of auto layout is necessary. See how to leverage auto layout in your presentation layer.
Discussion and examples of MVC and application resource organization

One of the difficult things to manage and scale is behavior related to DOM elements. See how Angular JS allows you to separate behavior into cohesive objects that can be easily applied to DOM elements.
